name: Invesco FTSE RAFI Canadian Index ETF
longDescription: PXC seeks to replicate to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the FTSE RAFI Canada Index, or any successor thereto. The ETF invests in equity securities of Canadian companies in order to replicate the FTSE RAFI Canada Index.
fulldescription: PXC seeks to replicate to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the FTSE RAFI Canada Index, or any successor thereto. The ETF invests in equity securities of Canadian companies in order to replicate the FTSE RAFI Canada Index. The index weights companies using four fundamental factors of company size: dividends cash flow, sales and book value
fullAddress: 5140 Yonge Street, Suite 900, Toronto, Ontario, CA
